Package: arframe
Title: A Submission-Native Clinical Report Builder
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Vignesh", "Thanikachalam", , "about.vignesh@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A local-first Shiny application for building clinical tables, listings,
    and figures against analysis-ready data, previewing them as submission-style
    output, and exporting reproducible reports. The interactive front end over the
    'arpillar' engine.
